snippet.title: Star Seeker in: the Secret of the Sorcerous Standoff (Announcement Trailer)
snippet.description:
Coming November 4th to Steam and itch.io!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1330930
Play the demo now: https://benedictide.itch.io/star-seeker-demo
Discord: https://discord.gg/hrx5mf
Twitter: https://twitter.com/StarSeekerGame

(Video production by Melissa Chaplin and Lucy Jones of Game If You Are. Voiceover narration by Justin McElroy.)
